OsmoBSC> enable

OsmoBSC# list
...
  vamos modify lchan <0-255> <0-255> <0-7> <0-1> [tsc] [<1-4>] [<0-7>]
...

OsmoBSC# vamos?
  vamos  Manually initiate VAMOS lchan multiplexing (for debugging)

OsmoBSC# vamos ?
  modify  Send Channel Mode Modify to change an lchan to prepare it for serving a second MS via VAMOS

OsmoBSC# vamos modify ?
  lchan  Pick a specific lchan to modify to VAMOS mode

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan ?
  <0-255>  BTS Number

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 ?
  <0-255>  TRX Number

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 ?
  <0-7>  Timeslot Number

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 0 ?
  <0-1>  Logical Channel Number

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 0 0 ?
  [tsc]  Provide specific TSC Set and Training Sequence Code

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 0 0 tsc ?
  [<1-4>]  TSC Set

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 0 0 tsc 1 ?
  [<0-7>]  Training Sequence Code

OsmoBSC# vamos modify lchan 0 0 0 0 tsc 1 0 ?
  <cr>  

OsmoBSC# configure terminal
OsmoBSC(config)# network
OsmoBSC(config-net)# list
...
  meas-feed destination ADDR <0-65535>
  meas-feed scenario NAME
...

OsmoBSC(config-net)# meas-feed destination 127.0.0.23 4223
OsmoBSC(config-net)# meas-feed scenario foo23
OsmoBSC(config-net)# show running-config
...
network
...
 meas-feed destination 127.0.0.23 4223
 meas-feed scenario foo23
...
